6
00:00:13,840 --> 00:00:15,540
A child in appearance with the I.Q. of an adult.

7
00:00:15,540 --> 00:00:17,540
His name is Detective Conan!

8
00:01:56,590 --> 00:01:58,390
Not once, but twice.

9
00:01:58,390 --> 00:02:01,590
Who are you, brave sir who has rescued me?

10
00:02:02,790 --> 00:02:05,390
Valiant nameless knight dressed in black.

11
00:02:05,390 --> 00:02:09,290
If you wish to grant me my wish,

12
00:02:09,290 --> 00:02:12,390
