17
00:02:25,290 --> 00:02:27,990
Good grief! Dad, be serious!

18
00:02:27,990 --> 00:02:30,690
There's not too much time left before my school play!

19
00:02:30,690 --> 00:02:32,090
Give me a break!

20
00:02:32,090 --> 00:02:34,090
Nobody can say these lines

21
00:02:34,090 --> 00:02:36,090
with a straight face, it's so unnatural.

22
00:02:36,090 --> 00:02:39,290
Who in the blazes wrote this syrupy script reading the script anyway?

23
00:02:39,290 --> 00:02:41,190
It was Sonoko!

24
00:02:41,190 --> 00:02:44,990
She said she wrote the part for the black knight with Shinichi in mind.

25
00:02:44,990 --> 00:02:46,090
That Sonoko...

26
00:02:46,090 --> 00:02:47,790
Hey, wait a minute!

27
00:02:47,790 --> 00:02:52,290
It says right here that the knight and princess kiss passionately!

28
00:02:52,290 --> 00:02:53,690
What?

29
00:02:53,690 --> 00:02:56,990
Oh, come on. It's just pretend, don't worry about it!

30
00:02:56,990 --> 00:02:58,490
Hey, Ran.

31
00:02:58,490 --> 00:03:00,690
Who's going to do it? You know, that knight's part.

32
00:03:00,690 --> 00:03:03,090
Why, are you that curious?

33
00:03:03,090 --> 00:03:05,390
Well, just a little...

34
00:03:05,390 --> 00:03:08,190
I'll bet you got some goofy kid to do the part.

35
00:03:08,190 --> 00:03:11,390
Actually, it's somebody you both know very well.

36
00:03:11,390 --> 00:03:13,590
Remember, you met him during one of your cases.

37
00:03:13,590 --> 00:03:15,190
It's our school doctor, Dr. Araide.

38
00:03:15,190 --> 00:03:17,290
All the boys in our school were too embarrassed to do it.

39
00:03:17,290 --> 00:03:20,190
So, we asked Dr. Araide when he came by to give us our physical exams.

40
00:03:20,190 --> 00:03:21,490
-Huh? -Huh?

41
00:03:21,490 --> 00:03:24,790
It seems he played a lot of leads in school plays in his days,

42
00:03:24,790 --> 00:03:26,090
that's why he's so good at it.

43
00:03:26,090 --> 00:03:28,890
He says the lines well and he knows how to handle women.

44
00:03:28,890 --> 00:03:30,890
Hey! I won't allow it!

45
00:03:30,890 --> 00:03:33,090
No, no! Don't do it, Ran

46
00:03:33,090 --> 00:03:34,490
Just kidding.

47
00:03:34,490 --> 00:03:37,690
He's just overlooking our rehearsals.

48
00:03:37,690 --> 00:03:41,990
Sonoko's going to dress like a man to play the part of the knight.

49
00:03:41,990 --> 00:03:43,790
Oh, I see.

50
00:03:43,790 --> 00:03:45,890
How stupid.

51
00:03:45,890 --> 00:03:47,190
Oh, no! Look at the time.

52
00:03:47,190 --> 00:03:49,590
I've got practice in the morning, so I've got to take a bath.

53
00:03:49,590 --> 00:03:51,490
The bath is not working.

54
00:03:51,490 --> 00:03:54,390
What? I wanted to take a bath, too

55
00:03:54,390 --> 00:03:57,090
Then, why don't you two go to the public bath?

56
00:03:57,090 --> 00:03:59,890
But I'm sure it's closed today.

57
00:03:59,890 --> 00:04:02,890
Why don't we go and ask Dr. Agasa to let us use his bath then?

58
00:04:02,890 --> 00:04:06,590
I was going there tonight anyway to talk about our camping trip this weekend.

59
00:04:06,590 --> 00:04:08,090
Really? Come on, let's go!

60
00:04:08,090 --> 00:04:09,690
I'll go get my change of clothes.

61
00:04:09,690 --> 00:04:11,490
Me, too.

62
00:04:11,490 --> 00:04:12,790
Good grief.

63
00:04:12,790 --> 00:04:14,800
You don't want to trouble the man too much,

64
00:04:14,820 --> 00:04:17,990
